  "title": "Jewelry Retail Sales (4.5 days workweek / Training Provided) (1358)",
  "description": "<p>Location: Central Region<br />\nSalary: $3000 - $4000 <br />\nWorking days: 4-5-4-5 days in rotation including PH, 10 off days per month <br />\nWorking hours: 10.30am to 9.45pm with 2 breaks<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Selling of gold jewellery, diamonds, and luxury goods</li><li>Attend to customers enquires and feedback</li><li>Provide excellent customer service and assistance to customers</li><li>Offer advice and guidance on product selections</li><li>Manage point-of-sale processes</li><li>Maintain good store condition and visual merchandising standards</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Must be willing to work on retail hours, weekend and public holiday</li><li>Keen in jewellery industry<br />\n     <br />\n     </li></ul><p>Or follow our instagram at:<br />\nhttps://www.instagram.com/thesupremehr/</p><p>Joel Toh Gim Long</p><p>\nThe Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd</p><p>\nEA No: 14C7279</p><p>\nReg No: R1441358</p>",
